text: Lauren Marlene Storm (born January 2, 1987) is an American actress. She acts in movies and television. She played Taylor Hagen in the TV show Flight 29 Down. She played Teresa Kilmer in the 2009 movie I Love You, Beth Cooper. Storm was born in Chicago.
